title: Did Biden Temporarily Freeze Trump Rule Lowering Insulin, EpiPen Prices?
subtitle: In his first week on the job, President Joe Biden issued more than a dozen executive orders.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: In the first days of his 2021 term, U.S. President Joe Biden temporarily froze a federal rule initiated by former President Donald Trump aimed at lowering insulin and EpiPen prices.
